{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 203, "title": "Fix non-pickleable retriever worker failures", "body": "## Summary\n- catch conversion failures inside process-pool workers so non-pickleable exceptions do not crash the whole retrieval batch\n- harden arXiv PDF/source downloads to degrade to warnings and allow fallback behavior\n- add a regression test covering a worker-raised `HTTPError` carrying a `BufferedReader`\n\n## Testing\n- uv run pytest -q tests/retriever/test_arxiv_retriever.py -k non_pickleable_worker_errors\n- uv run python -m compileall src tests/retriever/test_arxiv_retriever.py\n\nCloses #202", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "c2330b9cc071be37e918fcfa5d6e56ea98553bac", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "TideDra/zotero-arxiv-daily"}, "url": "https://github.com/TideDra/zotero-arxiv-daily/pull/203", "createdAt": "2026-03-18T06:34:41Z", "mergedAt": "2026-03-18T06:55:56Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "TideDra/zotero-arxiv-daily"}, "sha": "c2330b9cc071be37e918fcfa5d6e56ea98553bac"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/TideDra/zotero-arxiv-daily/pull/203.diff", "number": 203, "created_at": "2026-03-18T06:34:41Z", "merged_at": "2026-03-18T06:55:56Z", "resolved_issues": [202]}
